headline: Essex Property Trust (ESS) Valuation Check as Share Price Slides but Long-Term Returns Stay Positive
summary: Essex Property Trust (ESS) has quietly lagged the broader market this year, with the stock down about 8% year to date and roughly 11% over the past year, raising questions about valuation. See our latest analysis for Essex Property Trust. With the latest share price sitting at $257.57, Essex’s 1 year share price return remains negative while its multiyear total shareholder returns are still comfortably positive, suggesting momentum has cooled even as the longer term story remains intact.
